    "Doctor's TOSCA profile extends the OASIS standard basic Profile for NFV.",
    "It takes into account the particulars of the NDN.",
    "The orchestrator has been implemented from the ground up in order to provide it with the capability to comprehend and instantiate the various content-oriented components.",
    "(1) the deployment of NDN VNFs, classification of content, service chaining, and the definition of performance and security policies TOSCA templates make all of these things possible.",
